OL,3,CDeath, drought and devastation: Europe
OL,4,Cfaces 'huge number' of climate extremes
OL,6,FHow was Europe impacted by climate
OL,7,Fextremes in 2023? ITV News' Health &
OL,8,FScience Correspondent Martin Stew
OL,9,Fexplains the UN and EU report
OL,11,FHeat-related deaths have risen,
OL,12,Fwildfires the size of London, Paris
OL,13,Fand Berlin combined raged across
OL,14,FEurope, and the UK coastline faced a
OL,15,F"beyond extreme" marine heatwave in
OL,16,F2023, a climate report has found.
