OL,3,CDeath, drought and devastation: Europe
OL,4,Cfaces 'huge number' of climate extremes
OL,6,FEurope, including Britain, suffered a
OL,7,F"huge number" of climate extremes as
OL,8,Fthe continent was hit by heatwaves,
OL,9,Fwildfires, droughts and flooding last
OL,10,Fyear, EU and UN scientists have said.
OL,12,FExtreme weather has affected human
OL,13,Fhealth and caused billions of pounds
OL,14,Fin economic losses, and is set to
OL,15,Fworsen as the world warms, experts
OL,16,Fsaid as they launched a report on the
OL,17,FEuropean state of the climate in 2023.
OL,26,@oD@AOUoD@MO]
