OL,3,CDeath, drought and devastation: Europe
OL,4,Cfaces 'huge number' of climate extremes
OL,6,FThe report, from the EU's Copernicus
OL,7,FClimate Change Service (C3S) and the
OL,8,FUN's World Meteorological Service
OL,9,F(WMO), details the impacts of global
OL,10,Fwarming, including a "beyond extreme"
OL,11,Fmarine heatwave off the UK and Irish
OL,12,Fcoasts, the continent's largest ever
OL,13,Fwildfire and exceptional glacier melt.
OL,15,FHeat-related deaths are on the rise in
OL,16,FEurope, where it was found 63 lives
OL,17,Fwere lost to storms, 44 to floods and
OL,18,F44 to wildfires in 2023.
OL,26,@rD@VOUrD@eO]
