OL,4,Cfaces 'huge number' of climate extremes
OL,6,FWeather and climate-related economic
OL,7,Flosses totalled an estimated 13.4
OL,8,Fbillion euros (#11.5 billion), the
OL,9,Freport said.
OL,11,FCeleste Saulo, WMO secretary-general,
OL,12,Fsaid: "The climate crisis is the
OL,13,Fbiggest challenge of our generation.
OL,14,FThe cost of climate action may seem
OL,15,Fhigh but the cost of inaction is much
OL,16,Fhigher."
