OL,3,CDeath, drought and devastation: Europe
OL,4,Cfaces 'huge number' of climate extremes
OL,6,FOverall, the continent saw its joint
OL,7,Fwarmest or second warmest year on
OL,8,Frecord ` depending on the dataset used
OL,9,Ffor analysing the year ` with the
OL,10,Fwarmest September on record.
OL,12,FNorth western Europe saw its warmest
OL,13,FJune on record, while much of Europe
OL,14,Fwas hit by heatwaves during the
OL,15,F"extended summer" from June to
OL,16,FSeptember.
