OL,3,CDeath, drought and devastation: Europe
OL,4,Cfaces 'huge number' of climate extremes
OL,6,FHeat hit the oceans too, with the
OL,7,Faverage surface temperature for
OL,8,FEurope's seas the highest on record,
OL,9,Fthe report said.
OL,11,FAnd, in June, the Atlantic to the west
OL,12,Fof Ireland and around the United
OL,13,FKingdom was hit by a marine heatwave
OL,14,Fthat was classed as "extreme" and in
OL,15,Fsome areas "beyond extreme", with sea
OL,16,Fsurface temperatures up to 5C above
OL,17,Faverage.
