OL,3,CDeath, drought and devastation: Europe
OL,4,Cfaces 'huge number' of climate extremes
OL,6,FRainfall across Europe was up 7% on
OL,7,Faverage levels, with a third of the
OL,8,Friver network exceeding "high" flood
OL,9,Fthresholds and 16% seeing flows above
OL,10,Fthe "severe" flood threshold,
OL,11,Fincluding many rivers across the UK.
OL,13,FMajor river basins including the
OL,14,FLoire, Rhine and Danube saw record or
OL,15,Fnear-record high river flows due to a
OL,16,Fseries of storms between October and
OL,17,FDecember.
