OL,3,CDeath, drought and devastation: Europe
OL,4,Cfaces 'huge number' of climate extremes
OL,6,FFour fifths of the economic losses in
OL,7,F2023 were due to flooding, which
OL,8,Faffected an estimated 1.6 million
OL,9,Fpeople in Europe, the report said.
OL,11,FWildfires burned an area the size of
OL,12,FLondon, Paris and Berlin combined,
OL,13,Fwith Europe's largest ever fire in
OL,14,FGreece covering 370 square miles,
OL,15,Fwhile there were periods of drought in
OL,16,Fthe Iberian peninsula and eastern
OL,17,FEurope.
OL,1,Wz5~k4~k7}hw1 ~k4~sj5j5~s1 G     G9/14
