OL,3,CDeath, drought and devastation: Europe
OL,4,Cfaces 'huge number' of climate extremes
OL,6,F"We witnessed widespread floods, but
OL,7,Falso high temperature, extreme
OL,8,Fwildfire, severe drought.
OL,10,F"And these events have not only
OL,11,Fstrained natural ecosystems, but
OL,12,Fthey've also posed severe challenges
OL,13,Fto agriculture, water resources
OL,14,Fmanagement and public health.
OL,16,F"Hundreds of thousands of people were
OL,17,Faffected by extreme climate events in
OL,18,F2023, which have been responsible for
OL,19,Flarge losses at continental level,
OL,20,Festimated to be at least in the tens
OL,21,Fof billions of Euros," he said.
OL,26,@nD@AOUrD@AOUxD@AOU}D@VO]
