OL,3,CDeath, drought and devastation: Europe
OL,4,Cfaces 'huge number' of climate extremes
OL,6,F"Unfortunately, these figures are
OL,7,Funlikely to get smaller, at least in
OL,8,Fthe near future," he warned.
OL,10,FThe service's deputy director,
OL,11,FSamantha Burgess, said: "Europe in
OL,12,F2023 saw a huge number of records, a
OL,13,Frecord number of Europeans affected by
OL,14,Fheat stress, record ocean
OL,15,Ftemperatures, and record melting of
OL,16,Fglaciers.
OL,26,@nD@AOUpD@QO]sD@YOU
